{"tid":2428430,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook未經同意使用人臉辨識標籤　向160萬用戶賠償6.5億美元","createTime":"2021-03-01T14:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T15:31:16.000Z","uid":1086,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"897060e821861f252e49224da3db4eb8eb2b17ec","tid":2428430,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2889056/11_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2889056%2F11_1024.png&h=45c1eb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社交平台Facebook近年頻頻傳出醜聞，美國加州一名聯邦法官日前就批准Facebook（fb）以6.5億美元（約港幣50億元）和解一宗集體訴訟，事件涉fb未經用戶同意，使用人臉辨識技術在照片加標籤，法官形容這是其中一宗違反私隱法訴訟案件中最大筆的和解金額。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">集體訴訟由約160萬名伊利諾伊州Fb用戶於2015年發起，</span>他們指控fb在未徵求同意下，擅自蒐集用戶臉孔及指紋等數據，並為照片上的人臉自動加上標籤，違反伊利諾伊州《生物識別訊息私隱法》，事件最後轉由加州法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n法官在批准和解書上表示，和解方案將令每一位想要補償的集體訴訟者至少得到345美元（約港幣2,676元），形容是消費者在爭論激烈的數碼私隱方面的重大勝利。原告代表律師指出，若對方不提出上訴，支票將在兩周內寄出。"},{"pid":"8b1eb49987f88d74fc3850ddbcbd107c689ecf0c","tid":2428430,"uid":70888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"快點使用我"},{"pid":"a148e92b8137f33b6937d58af1c356a5367823d0","tid":2428430,"uid":120499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"香港冇集體訴訟權，屌你老母，垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca5b43ce2d1339c8180c52faa040e12db3560de","tid":2428430,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim